The 1st list of charges is for General Parking. 
The 2nd list of charges is for Terminal Direct Parking.

General Parking is available on seven floors of the Sea-Tac Airport garage - Floors 1-3, and 5-8. Parkers can use General Parking for both short- and long-term stays.

The fourth floor of the Parking Garage is reserved for Terminal Direct Parking.

For parking for more than 30 days you must make special arrangements through the Airport's Public Parking Office.

Passport Parking: 
monthly parking program for frequent travelers, $350.00/month for unlimited monthly parking on the terminal direct floor of the garage.

Motorcycles pay the same parking rates as automobiles for hourly, daily and weekly parking in both General and Terminal Direct parking.
